---
title: "auctionCallback (AuctionBidder)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_access: whenNotPaused
    q_access --> q_authCheck: msg.sender != address(s_auction) OR from != address(this)
    q_authCheck --> q_revert: unauthorized
    q_authCheck --> q_decode: authorized
    q_revert --> [*]: revert Errors.AccessForbidden()
    q_decode --> q_multiCall: calls = abi.decode(data, (Call[]))
    q_multiCall --> q_approve: _multiCall(calls)
    q_approve --> [*]: forceApprove(msg.sender, amountOut)

    note right of q_authCheck
        INV-001: only the stored auction contract can invoke callback
        INV-002: from must equal address(this) ensuring bid originated from this contract
    end note

    note right of q_multiCall
        INV-003: _multiCall executes arbitrary external calls decoded from data
        INV-004: after solving, contract approves exact amountOut to auction contract
    end note
